1. *Drugoga* dana ću kupiti novu knjigu. (On the *second* day I will buy a new book.)
2. Želim da čujem *drugoga* mišljenja pre nego što donesem odluku. (I want to hear *other* opinions before making a decision.)
3. *Drugoga* puta neću ponoviti istu grešku. (I won't make the same mistake the *next* time.)
4. *Drugoga* čoveka nisam videla od juče. (I haven't seen *another* person since yesterday.)
5. Oni se nikada ne razdvajaju jedan od *drugoga*. (They never separate from each *other*.)
6. Molim te da mi doneseš *drugoga* tanjira. (Please bring me *another* plate.)
7. *Drugoga* današnjeg sastanka neću moći prisustvovati. (I won't be able to attend *another* meeting today.)
8. Uvek misli na sebe i ne razmišlja o potrebama *drugoga*. (He always thinks of himself and doesn't consider *others'* needs.)
9. Ona se bavi humanitarnim radom kako bi pomogla *drugima*. (She engages in humanitarian work to help *others*.)
10. Nikada ne možeš znati šta se krije u mislima *drugih* ljudi. (You can never know what's hiding in *other* people's minds.)